self or anyone else (for example: telephone number, postal address, home address or email address or any other details that would allow you to be personally identified) in any FASHIONBEANS community.\r\n\r\n(iv) Legal requirements:\r\n* You may not submit or share any defamatory or illegal material of any nature in fashionbeans.com communities. This includes text, graphics, video, programs or audio.\r\n* Contributing material to a fashionbeans.com community with the intention of committing or promoting an illegal act is strictly prohibited.\r\n* You agree to submit to or share with fashionbeans.com communities only contributions which are your own original work. You must not violate, plagiarise, or infringe the rights of FashionBeans or third parties including copyright, trade mark, trade secrets, privacy, publicity, personal or proprietary rights.\r\n\r\n(v) If you’re under 16:\r\n* Please get a parent’s or guardian’s permission before taking part in any fashionbeans.com community.\r\n* Never reveal any personal information about yourself or anyone else (for example, school, telephone number, your full name, home address or email address).\r\n\r\n(vi) If you breach these Community Rules:\r\nIf you fail to abide by these Community Rules (and/or any variations in relevant local house rules) when taking part in a fashionbeans.com community, you will be sent an email which informs you why your contribution has been refused or edited. This email will also include a warning that continuing to break the rules may result in action being taken against your account or accounts.\r\n\r\nThis action may include any content posted by you being checked before allowed to go on the site or a temporary or permanent suspension of your ability to participate in any or all of fashionbeans.com community areas.\r\n\r\nIf you submit or share offensive or inappropriate content to or with any fashionbeans.com communities or anywhere else on fashionbeans.com or otherwise engage in any disrup