	(27, 1, '2013-03-22 13:53:18', '2013-03-22 13:53:18', '<h5>Louis Vuitton Spring/Summer 2013 Collection</h5>\r\nLouis Vuitton prepare us for the fast-approaching spring/summer 2013 season, with the release of their latest menswear lookbook.\r\n\r\nTaking influence from all things sport and nautical, the latest offering from the French fashion house features an exciting mix of casual staples alongside signature tailored pieces. From fitted blazers and classic suits to linen shirts, printed tees and cashmere pullovers the collection combines style with practicality and offers an outfit suitable for every occasion.\r\n\r\nCaptured on the stunning Eastern Africa coast, the lookbook really gets us in the mood for summer. Displaying all of your holiday necessities, from footwear and luggage to the stylish Louis Vuitton eyewear range, the lookbook showcases some of our most loved ensembles for the upcoming season.\r\n\r\nBold prints and vibrant hues add a fresh, contemporary edge to Louis Vuitton’s latest collection. Here at FashionBeans, we are really enjoying the use of bright orange throughout the line, and cannot wait to get our hands on a selection of our favourite pieces.\r\n\r\nMaintaining its strong focus on quality design and attention to detail, Louis Vuitton have delivered yet another great clothing collection, which oozes luxury and sophistication.\r\n\r\nThe collection will soon be available to purchase at select boutiques, so keep a look out.\r\n<h6>Louis Vuitton Spring/Summer 2013 Collection Lookbook</h6>\r\n<p align="center"><img alt="Louis Vuitton Spring/Summer 2013 Collection Lookbook" src="http://static.fashionbeans.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/lvss4.jpg" /></p>\r\n<p align="center"><img alt="Louis Vuitton Spring/Summer 2013 Collection Lookbook" src="http://static.fashionbeans.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/lvss5.jpg" /></p>\r\n<p align="center"><img alt="Louis Vuitton Spring/Summer 2013 Collection Lookbook" src="http://static.fashionbeans.com/wp-conte